        <updateDate>2020-02-10T22:30:14Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>State Allowance for a Variety of Exchanges Act or the SAVE Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to support the establishment of state-based health insurance exchanges in those states that have not already elected to do so. A state that receives a grant must ensure that the resulting exchange is self-sustaining by 2024. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
